16:10.603 --> 16:12.170
- Please let me go.

16:12.172 --> 16:14.205
- Ugh!
- Ahh, okay.

16:14.207 --> 16:15.473
What do you got in here?

16:15.475 --> 16:17.442
- Aah!
Just let me go!

16:17.444 --> 16:19.110
- Come on.

16:19.112 --> 16:20.278
- Aah!

16:20.280 --> 16:22.313
- Shh.
Hey, shh.

16:22.315 --> 16:24.682
- I haven't decided what to do
