16:24.684 --> 16:26.084
- I can think of things.

16:28.254 --> 16:29.587
- So boring.

16:32.359 --> 16:34.225
- Okay, look out. Look out.
Look out.

16:34.227 --> 16:36.995
Look out.
The whirlwind's coming.

16:36.997 --> 16:38.429
The white whirlwind's coming.

16:38.431 --> 16:41.032
You got to look out.
You got to look out.

16:41.034 --> 16:43.501
Look out.
The white whirlwind's coming.

16:43.503 --> 16:45.436
The whirlwind's coming.
The white whirlwind's coming.

16:45.438 --> 16:47.038
It's coming.
It's coming.

16:47.040 --> 16:48.773
Look out. Look out.
The white whirlwind.

16:48.775 --> 16:50.408
- Hey, are you Barry?
You Barry?

16:50.410 --> 16:52.210
Your wife's looking for you,
man.

16:52.212 --> 16:54.312
- The white whirlwind.
- Your wife is looking for you.

16:54.314 --> 16:57.248
[whooshing]

16:59.352 --> 17:00.718
Barry!

17:00.720 --> 17:03.421
- Ah, the white whirlwind!
It's coming!

17:03.423 --> 17:05.590
- Don't go in there.
