17:05.592 --> 17:07.792
- You can't.
You can't.

17:07.794 --> 17:09.494
[Barry screams]

17:11.331 --> 17:13.664
- Aah!
[sobbing]

17:14.768 --> 17:16.601
Barry!

17:18.038 --> 17:20.071
[sobbing]

17:20.073 --> 17:22.774
My Barry.
[sobbing]

