- [grunts]

17:27.447 --> 17:29.347
Run.

17:29.349 --> 17:32.583
- All right,
it's time for one more shot.

17:32.585 --> 17:34.352
We got this.

17:34.354 --> 17:35.620
- [grunts]

17:35.622 --> 17:36.821
<i> [mysterious chirping]</i>

17:36.823 --> 17:39.090
[gunfire]

17:39.092 --> 17:41.109
<i> - We don't know what's</i>
