17:58.344 --> 17:59.410
- An adept.

17:59.412 --> 18:00.645
[glass shatters]

18:00.647 --> 18:03.648
- [muttering]

18:03.650 --> 18:06.651
- And it goes in

18:06.653 --> 18:09.087
about that much.

18:09.089 --> 18:10.388
Okay.

18:10.390 --> 18:12.857
<i> [dark music]</i>

18:12.859 --> 18:14.792
Dad. Dad.
Dad! No!

18:14.794 --> 18:16.828
- No, you won't get me!
- Dad! No!

18:16.830 --> 18:22.633
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

18:25.205 --> 18:27.338
- I'm sorry.
I don't want to leave,

18:27.340 --> 18:28.539
but I have something important.

18:28.541 --> 18:30.608
- Nothing's important.

18:30.610 --> 18:31.742
- That's why I don't want
to leave.

18:31.744 --> 18:33.111
You'll do it again.

18:33.113 --> 18:35.146
- Soon as I can get
back up there.

18:35.148 --> 18:36.881
- Why?

18:36.883 --> 18:38.850
- Self-hate. End of the world.
You pick.

18:40.720 --> 18:42.353
- You have tetracycline?

18:42.355 --> 18:43.588
- Town's fresh out.

18:43.590 --> 18:45.690
- Sorry.

