I don't want to leave you alone,
but I need tetra.

18:48.561 --> 18:49.894
You know, we're all going
through shit,

18:49.896 --> 18:51.195
but we're not trying
to off ourselves.

18:51.197 --> 18:52.897
- I did something.
- What?

18:56.736 --> 18:57.635
- Doesn't matter.

19:00.273 --> 19:01.672
- Talk fast.

19:03.810 --> 19:05.877
- I hung with the same crew
since tenth grade,

19:05.879 --> 19:08.279
and when the end of days hit,
we just kept having fun.

19:08.281 --> 19:09.914
- So?

19:09.916 --> 19:12.216
- Yesterday, my friend Kimmy
started raving.

19:12.218 --> 19:14.452
She attacked Jaimo.
She was apeshit.

19:14.454 --> 19:16.787
- She had the plague.

19:16.789 --> 19:18.556
- That's what I thought.

19:18.558 --> 19:22.260
So when she came at me,
I shot her in the head, twice.

19:22.262 --> 19:23.461
She was my friend.

19:23.463 --> 19:25.263
- Hey, you had to.

19:25.265 --> 19:27.298
- No, I didn't have to.

19:27.300 --> 19:29.233
She wasn't a Feverhead.
She just ate something bad,

19:29.235 --> 19:32.837
like molly or bath salts
or some shit like that, and...

19:32.839 --> 19:34.639
I killed her.

19:35.875 --> 19:37.208
- [grunting]

19:38.244 --> 19:39.377
- I'm sorry.

19:39.379 --> 19:40.778
But I got to go.

19:45.318 --> 19:46.651
Same thing happened to me.

19:46.653 --> 19:47.952
I know what you are.

19:47.954 --> 19:49.487
- I know what you are too.

19:49.489 --> 19:50.488
[gunshot]

19:50.490 --> 19:52.790
[groaning]

19:52.792 --> 19:54.358
- Show yourself!

19:59.933 --> 20:02.333
He wasn't possessed.

20:02.335 --> 20:03.601
He was just off his meds.

20:06.573 --> 20:07.972
It isn't your fault.

20:09.809 --> 20:11.676
You don't need to hurt yourself.

20:11.678 --> 20:13.277
- Jury's out.

20:17.250 --> 20:19.650
- Come with me.

20:19.652 --> 20:21.485
- Who are you trying to save?

20:21.487 --> 20:22.987
- My father.
There's a mall this way, right?

20:22.989 --> 20:24.355
- Not much of one, but yeah.

20:24.357 --> 20:25.423
- Come with me.

20:27.393 --> 20:29.827
- I don't think so.

20:29.829 --> 20:32.496
But hey, you're on the clock,
so I--

20:32.498 --> 20:34.332
I won't try and do it again.

20:34.334 --> 20:36.500
You don't have to worry
about me, okay?

20:38.304 --> 20:39.303
- Fine.

20:39.305 --> 20:42.306
<i> [dark music]</i>

20:42.308 --> 20:49.280
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

20:52.652 --> 20:54.952
<i> - [whispering]</i>
<i> You're not a child anymore.</i>

