24:22.829 --> 24:24.762
- So?
- It's tetra.

24:24.764 --> 24:26.063
I have it.

24:28.468 --> 24:29.700
- Come on.

24:33.172 --> 24:36.474
<i> - Like sand through the</i>
<i>hourglass, my fellow travelers,</i>

24:36.476 --> 24:38.876
<i>the first grains of the wounded</i>
<i> moon are suckered in</i>

24:38.878 --> 24:40.945
<i> by Mother Earth's</i>
<i> fatal attraction,</i>

