<i>So dig the still and eerie calm</i>
<i> of resignation</i>

24:49.021 --> 24:51.255
<i> shot through</i>
<i> with a million little tales</i>

24:51.257 --> 24:53.724
<i> of final desperation.</i>

24:54.827 --> 24:56.126
- [breathing heavily]

24:56.128 --> 24:57.828
Sorry about the running,
but we're out of time.

24:57.830 --> 25:00.030
- I can handle it.

25:05.071 --> 25:06.670
- Wait, wait, wait, wait,
wait, wait.

25:06.672 --> 25:09.073
- What are you doing?
- It's a sign.

25:09.075 --> 25:10.274
Okay.

25:10.276 --> 25:13.143
Are you coming?

25:13.145 --> 25:14.845
- Yeah.
- Let's go.

25:27.593 --> 25:30.528
- [muttering]

25:32.098 --> 25:33.831
Oh.

25:33.833 --> 25:36.133
Oh, hey, Dana.

25:36.135 --> 25:37.668
It's me, Dad.

25:37.670 --> 25:39.303
- I'm not Dana.
I'm Sherry.

25:39.305 --> 25:42.039
- Yes, you are.
Dana.

25:42.041 --> 25:43.841
We named you Dana.

25:46.579 --> 25:47.878
Where's your sister?

25:47.880 --> 25:49.980
- I don't have a sister.

25:49.982 --> 25:51.749
- Hm?

25:51.751 --> 25:53.017
Yes, you do.

25:53.019 --> 25:55.185
Don't say that.

25:55.187 --> 25:57.321
She makes me mad sometimes too.

25:57.323 --> 25:58.989
- Are you a Feverhead?

25:58.991 --> 26:00.991
- No.

26:00.993 --> 26:03.193
No.
I was...

26:03.195 --> 26:04.795
brought up Presbyterian,

26:04.797 --> 26:07.197
but my father...
said something.

26:07.199 --> 26:11.101
It was important,
but I can't remember.

26:11.103 --> 26:13.804
[machine gun firing]
- [screaming]

26:13.806 --> 26:16.240
- On your feet.
Up. Up!

26:16.242 --> 26:17.675
[gun firing]
[girl screaming]

26:17.677 --> 26:19.176
Get away from the girl,
Feverhead.

26:19.178 --> 26:20.277
- No, no, it's fine.
It's okay.

26:20.279 --> 26:21.879
- I knew it!

26:21.881 --> 26:23.347
- Guys, it's the--
one and the many--

26:23.349 --> 26:25.015
- Oh, there's no doubt
on this one.

26:25.017 --> 26:27.318
- Signs and portents.
Signs and portents.

26:29.655 --> 26:31.288
- Feverhead.

26:31.290 --> 26:33.691
Knew it.

26:33.693 --> 26:35.993
- Yes.
